tr.th:
Modelling
            from agricultural practices data (e.g., Lindner and Koch,
            2022)

list-item.p:
The farm has the same PACAGE number in FADN and AC: then
          the LPIS plots with this PACAGE number are associated with
          that FADN-AC-FQS farm;

sec.p:
The number of uncovered days is then calculated as

        366 - \textrm{number of covered days}
        366−number of covered days.

